OL,3,CData watchdog reprimands Hackney
OL,4,CCouncil over cyber attack
OL,6,FThe UK's data protection regulator has
OL,7,Fissued a reprimand to the London
OL,8,FBorough of Hackney over its handling
OL,9,Fof a cyber attack.
OL,11,FThe Information Commissioner's Office
OL,12,F(ICO) said the council had "failed to
OL,13,Feffectively implement sufficient
OL,14,Fmeasures" to protect its systems from
OL,15,Fattack.
