OL,3,CData watchdog reprimands Hackney
OL,4,CCouncil over cyber attack
OL,6,FThe borough was targeted by hackers in
OL,7,FOctober 2020 in an attack which saw
OL,8,Fcyber criminals gain access to and
OL,9,Fencrypt 440,000 files, affecting at
OL,10,Fleast 280,000 residents and other
OL,11,Findividuals. It included personal
OL,12,Finformation related to religious
OL,13,Fbeliefs, health, criminal records,
OL,14,Feconomic data and details of sexual
OL,15,Forientation, among other personal
OL,16,Fidentifiers.
