OL,3,CData watchdog reprimands Hackney
OL,4,CCouncil over cyber attack
OL,6,FAccording to the ICO, more than 9,600
OL,7,Frecords were exfiltrated from the
OL,8,Fcouncil's systems, which posed a
OL,9,F"meaningful risk of harm" to 230
OL,10,Fpeople.
OL,12,FThe ICO said the cyber attack also
OL,13,Fsubstantially disrupted the council's
OL,14,Foperations, with some services not
OL,15,Freturning to normal until 2022.
