OL,3,CData watchdog reprimands Hackney
OL,4,CCouncil over cyber attack
OL,6,FIn its investigation into the breach,
OL,7,Fthe data protection regulator found
OL,8,Fsecurity patches had not been properly
OL,9,Fapplied to all devices, and the
OL,10,Fcouncil had failed to change an
OL,11,Finsecure password on a dormant account
OL,12,Fthat was still connected to its
OL,13,Fservers, which was exploited by the
OL,14,Fhackers.
