OL,3,CData watchdog reprimands Hackney
OL,4,CCouncil over cyber attack
OL,6,FStephen Bonner, deputy commissioner of
OL,7,Fthe ICO, said: "This was a clear and
OL,8,Favoidable error from London Borough of
OL,9,FHackney, one that has resulted in a
OL,10,Fmass loss of data and has had a
OL,11,Fseverely detrimental impact on many
OL,12,Fresidents.
OL,14,F"At its absolute worst, this has meant
OL,15,Fthat some of the most deeply personal
OL,16,Finformation possible has ended up in
OL,17,Fthe hands of the attackers.
OL,26,@oD@POUvD@AOU
