OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F407A1721318075
OL,3,CData watchdog reprimands Hackney
OL,4,CCouncil over cyber attack
OL,6,F"Systems that people rely on were
OL,7,Foffline for many months. This is
OL,8,Fentirely unacceptable and should not
OL,9,Fhave happened.
OL,11,F"Whilst nefarious actors may always
OL,12,Fexist, the council failed to
OL,13,Feffectively implement
OL,15,Fsufficient measures that could have
OL,16,Fbetter protected their systems and
OL,17,Fdata from cyber attacks.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
