OL,3,CData watchdog reprimands Hackney
OL,4,CCouncil over cyber attack
OL,6,F"Anyone responsible for protecting
OL,7,Fpersonal data should not make simple
OL,8,Fmistakes like having dormant accounts
OL,9,Fwhere the username and password are
OL,10,Fthe same. Time and time again, we see
OL,11,Fbreaches that would not have happened
OL,12,Fif such mistakes were avoided.
OL,14,F"If we want people to have trust in
OL,15,Flocal authorities, they need to trust
OL,16,Fthat local authorities will look after
OL,17,Ftheir data properly.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
