OL,3,CData watchdog reprimands Hackney
OL,4,CCouncil over cyber attack
OL,6,F"Hackney residents have learnt the
OL,7,Fhard way the consequences for these
OL,8,Ferrors ` councils across the country
OL,9,Fshould act now to ensure that those
OL,10,Fthey are responsible for do not suffer
OL,11,Fthe same fate."
OL,13,FFollowing the attack, the ICO said the
OL,14,Fborough took a number of remedial
OL,15,Fsteps, including ensuring all
OL,16,Fresidents were aware of the incident
OL,17,Fand promptly engaging with the
OL,18,Frelevant authorities.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@OO]
