OL,3,CData watchdog reprimands Hackney
OL,4,CCouncil over cyber attack
OL,6,FThe regulator also acknowledged the
OL,7,Fcouncil had sought to update its
OL,8,Fsecurity patch management system prior
OL,9,Fto the attack, the impact of the Covid-
OL,10,F19 pandemic on the council's staff and
OL,11,Fresources, and it commended the
OL,12,Fborough for its good governance
OL,13,Fstructures.
OL,15,FIt said because of this and the
OL,16,Fpositive actions taken by Hackney
OL,17,Fcouncil to mitigate harm, a reprimand
OL,18,Fhas been issued rather than a fine.
