OL,6,F"The council took swift and
OL,7,Fcomprehensive action to mitigate the
OL,8,Fharm of the attack as soon as it
OL,9,Flearned it had taken place, including
OL,10,Fthrough their engagement with NCSC
OL,11,F(The National Cyber Security Centre),
OL,12,Fand has taken a number of positive
OL,13,Fsteps since," Mr Bonner said.
